com.interpss.core.algo.dclf.adapter

Interface DclfAlgoBus

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BusRef<AclfBus>, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DclfAlgoBusImpl

    public interface DclfAlgoBus
extends BusRef<AclfBus>
    A representation of the model object 'Dclf Algo Bus'. Class for defining a bus object for storing Dclf algorithm results. The DclfAlgoBus.id should be the same as the corresponding AclfBus.id for persistance.

    The following features are supported:

    • Gen Adjust
    • Load Adjust
    • Gen List
    • Load List
    See Also:
    DclfAlgoAdapterPackage.getDclfAlgoBus()
